       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6CL04.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-CLOSURE-RECORD.
           05  WS-WORK-DAYS-TO-CLOSE PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-EXCESS-WORK-DAYS   PIC S9(5) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-AMOUNT-DUE         PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-WORK-DAYS-TO-CLOSE
           PERFORM 2300-ASSESS-PENALTY
           DISPLAY WS-AMOUNT-DUE
           STOP RUN.
       2300-ASSESS-PENALTY.
           COMPUTE WS-EXCESS-WORK-DAYS =
              WS-WORK-DAYS-TO-CLOSE - 7
           IF WS-EXCESS-WORK-DAYS IS POSITIVE
              COMPUTE WS-AMOUNT-DUE =
                 500 * WS-EXCESS-WORK-DAYS
           ELSE
              MOVE ZERO TO WS-AMOUNT-DUE
           END-IF.
